<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="area-n">area <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'eəriə/    美 /'eriə/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>地区；地带：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an industrial area
工业区</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the area code
区号</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>场所；地方：</strong></h4>
<p>a part of a room, building or particular space that is used for a special purpose：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a non-smoking / <strong>no-smoking area</strong>
无烟区/禁烟区</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>reception area</strong> of the hotel
酒店接待处</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a play / parking / dining area</strong>
游戏场地/停车场/用餐处</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>面积：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The island covered an area of 800 square kilometers.
这座岛占地面积为800平方公里。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>领域；范围：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Choosing the right food has become an area of study in modern life.
选择适当的食物已成为现代生活的一个研究领域。</p></div></div>